{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":190,"question":"老王凭借手艺开了一家修鞋店，但近年来找他修鞋的人越来越少、生意越来越差，老王很是苦恼。在儿子小王的建议下，他购进了设备，将修鞋店改成鞋子干洗、保养的店，生意又变得红火了。<br/><br/>小王的建议体现了SCAMPER中的哪些思维？","type":2,"analysis":"Substitute 用鞋子干洗、保养业务代替维修<br/>Adapt 适应了人们生活水平提高、修鞋需求变少、保养需求增加的现状","pic":null,"difficulty":3,"knowledgeId":15,"sceneId":1,"del":true,"problemId":3,"sequence":13,"example":false,"practiceUid":"T003C002F003X01013","score":50,"choiceList":[{"id":604,"questionId":190,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":605,"questionId":190,"subject":"Combine合并","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":606,"questionId":190,"subject":"Adapt适应","sequence":3,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":607,"questionId":190,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":4,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":627,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":446,"comment":"同意，修改是要建立在原有的基础上的，修鞋店的服务原本是修鞋，而现在是干洗和保养，修鞋服务完全被替代了，修改也就没有基础了。","openid":null,"addTime":1488692013000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"个人理解修改是针对产品或服务本身进行调整改动，但本题中，并没有提到对修鞋工艺或服务有什么改动，而且增加了服务品种。","del":0,"repliedName":"Yanae Yang","name":"大头娃娃","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNEvKRFpbeOmYHJcFmkdv2hiaKchUpf7g590IA9HhXv7c4GmX8j4jP25LT0ATygpmZwibqTTOBtHta/0","discussTime":"2017-03-05"},{"id":616,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":399,"comment":"+1","openid":null,"addTime":1488629824000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么没有修改","del":0,"repliedName":"晓露sheri","name":"八戒","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQE8wJ7qQSJTlmaTJcTpaQUDoCs6iaFkricgianiaPnqibdWLBibGmu1of7mDBeXib5lVAkgQ6Z0MiaUG6WiaQ/0","discussTime":"2017-03-04"},{"id":446,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":399,"comment":"个人理解修改是针对产品或服务本身进行调整改动，但本题中，并没有提到对修鞋工艺或服务有什么改动，而且增加了服务品种。","openid":null,"addTime":1488355910000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么没有修改","del":0,"repliedName":"晓露sheri","name":"Yanae Yang","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03G